            "title": "南山鋁業折讓6.39%配股籌20億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">南山鋁業(02610)公布，擬配股集資約20億元；每股作價64.5元，較該股昨天收市價68.9元折讓6.39%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"南山鋁業2025年度中期報告封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/02610.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"南山鋁業2025年度中期報告封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/02610.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">南山鋁業2025年度中期報告封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價66.22元計，配股價較之折讓2.6%；較前10個交易日平均收市價63元則折讓2.38%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集資淨額約19.87億元，90%用於潛在電解鋁及相關原材料以及輔助業務；10%用於一般營運資金。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15602210-%e5%8d%97%e5%b1%b1%e9%8b%81%e6%a5%ad%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%936-39%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c20%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/02610-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-22 09:25:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
